<item>
            <title>[SOLR-16540] Fix errors importing main and branch_9x into eclipse</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16540</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When creating an eclipse project using the eclipse gradle target, the resulting project has errors.  One is because there is a duplicate class name, the others are having package-info.java in the test code tree in addition to the main code tree for the same package.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The patch I will attach fixes the errors.  There are thousands of warnings, something for another issue.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
