&lt;p&gt;I think its a side effect of find/replace potentially?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17688702" author="alex.parvulescu" created="Tue, 14 Feb 2023 21:00:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=elyograg&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;elyograg&quot;&gt;elyograg&lt;/a&gt; hope you don&apos;t mind, I put up a PR for this change. there were some more style checks failing which I added to gradle ignores&#160; &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/solr/pull/1357&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/solr/pull/1357&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I still could not figure out the source problem, but at least this gets Eclipse import working without any errors.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
